    "department": "Engineering",
    "description": "AMBITIOUS TALENT WANTED\n\n\nSilver.dev has clients and would-be clients willing and able to sponsor immigration visas to the United States. The visas include O1, J1 visas and possibly L1 for future clients, depending on the interests and profile of candidates and companies.\n\nCandidates who wish to achieve this need to compete head-to-head with American talent and beat them aggressively in quality. This is also a journey of uncertainty, hardship, and personal transformation.\n\nOnly the most technically proficient candidates with the most clear resolve have the slightest chance of making it happen.\n\n\nIf that's you, come to Silver to prove it.\n\n\nREQUIREMENTS\n\n - C1 English or Above\n\n - 90 %+ pass rate on LC medium level challenges under 45 minutes.\n\n - Fully fluent in end-to-end application development. Leaning FE or BE is ok.\n\n - Exceptional traits: open source contributions, successful product launches, distinguished achievements or rocket-ship career track\n\n\nPROCESS\n\n - A superb application for this position is required\n\n - A live coding session with Gabriel Benmergui\n\n\nOnly after passing the live coding will the positions and the companies be discussed in detail.\n\n\nHOW IMMIGRATION TO THE US WORKS\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
